  <mainDescription>&lt;p>&#xD;
    &lt;font face=&quot;Arial, sans-serif&quot;>&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;>The goal of this task is to define a technical approach that fulfills&#xD;
    project requirements within the constraints of the system and development team. The architect should complete the&#xD;
    following:&lt;/font>&lt;/font>&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;p style=&quot;MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0in&quot;>&#xD;
            &lt;font face=&quot;Arial, sans-serif&quot;>&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;>&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;>&lt;span style=&quot;FONT-STYLE: normal&quot;>&lt;span&#xD;
            style=&quot;FONT-WEIGHT: normal&quot;>Work with the team to create an initial sketch of the technical approach to the&#xD;
            proposed system&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/font>&lt;/font>&lt;/font>&#xD;
        &lt;/p>&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;p style=&quot;MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0in&quot;>&#xD;
            &lt;font face=&quot;Arial, sans-serif&quot;>&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;>&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;>&lt;span style=&quot;FONT-STYLE: normal&quot;>&lt;span&#xD;
            style=&quot;FONT-WEIGHT: normal&quot;>Ensure that the technical decisions are adequately captured and&#xD;
            communicate&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/font>&lt;/font>&lt;/font>&#xD;
        &lt;/p>&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;p style=&quot;MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0in&quot;>&#xD;
            &lt;font face=&quot;Arial, sans-serif&quot;>&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;>&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;>&lt;span style=&quot;FONT-STYLE: normal&quot;>&lt;span&#xD;
            style=&quot;FONT-WEIGHT: normal&quot;>Ensure that the team has enough information to understand the approach that your&#xD;
            are taking&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/font>&lt;/font>&lt;/font>&#xD;
        &lt;/p>&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul></mainDescription>
